{"tid":1312089,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣]  警隊不遵守火器及彈藥條例","createTime":"2019-07-13T12:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T12:35:44.000Z","uid":191474,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"39a221390ffc9e6d2e6185135c12df5ec6d89556","tid":1312089,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:22:39.000Z","msg":"根據 <span style=\"color: red;\">胡椒噴劑的管有受《火器及彈藥條例》</span>（第２３８章）規管。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警隊一向有安全的守則及指引，所有配備胡椒噴劑的前線人員都需接受適當的訓練，確保人員清楚了解相關的安全指引。警務人員如使用胡椒噴劑，須確保在符合<span style=\"color: red;\">使用最低程度武力的原則下方可使用</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201304/24/P201304240282.htm[img][/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201304%2F24%2FP201304240282.htm%5Bimg%5D%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK99ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=95e66408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201304/24/P201304240282.htm[img][/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oG6vZgv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoG6vZgv.jpg&h=5e81715b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d2195d79205f4f9aaa3adfc2f7632416e7b87fd","tid":1312089,"uid":1550,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:24:17.000Z","msg":"死黑警犯撚哂法"},{"pid":"57ba22c322470a0c2f69f26287d10d847a933352","tid":1312089,"uid":199425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:25:40.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bac1aa3ad5a7a18ca75c3e98ae1fc89a4533d1","tid":1312089,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:28:10.000Z","msg":"補link<br />\n<br />\nsorry我又會咁柒都有既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><b